scirun v5 prototype build instructions

required:

	Visual C++ 2010 or gcc 4.6 (?).

	Boost 1.49
		uses these compiled libraries: 
			date_time
			filesystem
			graph
			regex
			serialization
			signals
			system
			thread

	CMake 2.8
		Root cmake file is SCIRunGUIPrototype/src/CMakeLists.txt.
		Make sure BUILD_SHARED_LIBS is on.

	Qt 4.7.4

optional:

	Vtk 5.10 
		build using CMake: turn option VTK_USE_QT on
	Once vtk is built, in the SCIRunGUIPrototype/src/CMakeLists.txt file, turn on option VTK_SUPPORT, and make sure VTK_DIR is set correctly.
